{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bb1dfe70da","title":"关于注意各地发生强迫命令、违法乱纪问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1955184e3c","index":0,"year":1958,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"bb1dfe70da"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"58aeb5365d","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共湖北省委第一书记王任重1958年11月28日向毛泽东报送的"},{"id":"342b5ce021","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"251f5d64b1","type":"title","text":"关于注意各地发生强道命令、违法乱纪问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da"},{"id":"58aeb5365d","type":"paragraph","text":"最近几期新华通讯社的《内部参考》，载了许多件各地（一部分人民公社）发生强追命令，违法乱纪的材料，很值得看一下，请各同志予以注意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da"},{"id":"342b5ce021","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da"},{"id":"c73a000586","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年十二月一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da"},{"id":"808a21dbd6","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请小平刚同志印发。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da"},{"id":"91b9793691","type":"paragraph","text":"毛关于湖北省随县金屯乡干部弄虚作假，搞“六万斤卫星”试验田情况的报告。报告说，今年9月，随县县委在得知金屯乡光大九社的一亩中稻试验田放出六万斤的“卫星”后，到现场调查，结果发现，这块试验田是乡社的一些负责人强迫群众用一天一夜时间将9.75亩中稻拔掉移栽上去的。问题弄清后，县委对这个乡进行了整顿，并对有关干部作了处理。现在干部的作风有了很大转变。毛泽东的批语及这个报告作为中共八届六中全会文件在会上印发。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da"}],"page":{"id":"689a2ba828","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"bb1dfe70da","start":55,"end":56}}}},"__N_SSG":true}